{{wikipedia}}
==English==
===Noun===
'''tobacco''' ([[uncountable]])

#any plant of the genus Nicotiana 
#leaves of certain varieties of the plant (cultivated and harvested to make [[cigarette]]s, [[cigar]]s, [[snuff]], for smoking in [[pipe]]s or for [[chew]]ing.


